doctype html
html(ng-app='musicblog')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/resources/styles/css/styles.css')
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Julius+Sans+One', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(rel='stylesheet' href='/resources/styles/css/pure-min.css')
    title Some great name
  body
    #main.pure-g
      header.pure-u-1
        div
          a(href='/')
            h1 Music Review Blog
            h2 music|coding|music|design|music
        div.social
          a.pure-u-1-4.social(href='http://facebook.com/fabian.potschies', target='_blank')
            div
              img(src='/resources/images/icons/facebook.svg')
          a.pure-u-1-4.social(href='404')
            div
              img(src='/resources/images/icons/googleplus.svg')
          a.pure-u-1-4.social
              div
                  img(src='/resources/images/icons/twitter.svg')
          a.pure-u-1-4.social(href='http://last.fm/user/wearethewinds', target='_blank')
            div
              img(src='/resources/images/icons/lastfm.svg')
      div(ng-view='')
      section#about
        .fontwrapper
          .title.pure-u-1
            h1 Anything else
        .heightwrapper
          .pure-u-1-2.lightorange
            h2 About me
            p
              | My name is Fabian, music addict, drummer, coder, currently living in Hamburg. Music has been a passion for since being six years old, dancing to the records of my parents (Pink Floyd, Wishbone Ash, Canned Heat...) The obscure, the psychedelic, the raw is still something that can be found in my nowadays music taste, ranging from folk, heavy metal to silence set to music.
          .pure-u-1-2.heavenblue
            h2 Special thanks to
            p
              a(href='http://www.colourlovers.com/lover/manekineko', target='_blank') manekineko
              | for the colour palette.
            p
              a(href='http://www.colourlovers.com/', target='_blank') Colourlovers
              | for letting manekineko create his color palette
            p
              | And some arbitrary greetings to:
              br
              a(href='http://www.friederloch.de', target='_blank') Frieder
              | , Martin, Rafael, Manuel, Nico, Sebastian, David, Sven, Desy, Jana, Malaika
